[Over one day, the number of suspected cases has gone from 9 to 28 and will likely increase further. The serotype of _S. enterica_ and suspected vehicle have not yet been reported. - Mod.LL

For photos of the church and barbecue helpers see ProMED archive Salmonellosis - USA (16): (NC) church barbecue 20130918.1953692

